#About This Program
-------------------

This program is a fun little "game" that allows a community to develop a "choose your own adventure" game. Its very simple, and probably could be recreated easily. However, we hope that our version fits your bill just fine.

-------------------
#Changelog
-------------------

2009-12-18 12:30AM
--"Paradox Edition" of the Choose Your Own Adventure script forked from IAMCAL.COM and released under GPL with permission. Current changes are limited to including an installer script, and the origional script which is the only one that is working. 

